HEADWORD: Zoocyst
<hw>Zo"o*cyst</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[<ets>Zoo-</ets> +
<ets>cyst</ets>.]</ety> <fld>(Biol.)</fld> <def>A cyst formed by certain
